description: A flourless cupcake that is light and fluffy with the secret ingredient of cannellini beans.
keywords: Cupcake,Pescatarian,Seafood free,Soy free,Wheat free,Gluten free,Vegetarian,Sesame free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Cannellini Bean Cupcakes Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Before serving dust with icing sugar. Enjoy!
Line a 12 cupcake baking tin with cupcake liners. Set aside.

In a food processor add cannellini beans, vanilla essence, salt and raw sugar, process for 5 minutes or until you get a smooth consistency. Then add eggs and process for a further 2 minutes until well combined.
In a stainless steel bowl transfer mixture and add almond meal. Fold in gently until well combined.
Divide batter into the 12 cupcake lined tin and bake for 20 minutes or until skewer comes out clean.
Remove from oven let cool in tin for 10 minutes until transferring to cooling rack.
